<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Smart Agriculture App</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    background:#f4f6f9;
}

header{
    background:#2c7be5;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

nav{
    background:#1b4f9c;
    padding:10px;
    text-align:center;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin:0 15px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

nav a:hover{
    text-decoration:underline;
}

.container{
    padding:30px;
    display:flex;
    gap:30px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    width:300px;
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    border-radius:8px;
}

button{
    background:#28a745;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    padding:10px 20px;
    margin-top:10px;
    border-radius:5px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover{
    background:#218838;
}

/* Alert button section */
.alert-section{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px;
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
    background:#2c7be5;
    color:white;
    margin-top:30px;
}
</style>

<script>
function showAlert(){
    alert("Welcome! This Smart Agriculture App helps farmers monitor crops using technology.");
}
</script>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Smart Agriculture Monitoring System</h1>
<p>Using Technology to Improve Farming</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Services</a>
<a href="#">About</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef">
<h2>Crop Monitoring</h2>
<p>This module helps farmers monitor crop health using sensors and real-time data analytics.</p>
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smart_farming" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
<br>
<button onclick="showAlert()">Click Me</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464226184884-fa280b87c399">
<h2>Weather Prediction</h2>
<p>The system provides weather updates to help farmers make better irrigation and farming decisions.</p>
<a href="https://www.weather.com" target="_blank">Weather Info</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1471193945509-9ad0617afabf">
<h2>IoT Sensors</h2>
<p>IoT sensors collect soil moisture, temperature, and humidity data to improve crop productivity.</p>
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_of_things" target="_blank">About IoT</a>
</div>

</div>

<!-- ALERT BUTTON SECTION -->
<div class="alert-section">
<h2>Interactive Feature</h2>
<p>Click the button below to see an alert message.</p>
<button onclick="showAlert()">Show Alert Message</button>
</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Internship Project | Smart Agriculture App</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>